    <item>
      <title>Milei 的休克疗法已经让投资者渴望更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/milei-s-shock-therapy-already-leaves-investors-craving-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱政府上任仅两天就宣布了 10 项新措施，以帮助阿根廷经济摆脱困境。对于那些因这位煽动性总统的承诺而推动该国资产上涨的投资者来说，这可能微不足道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/milei-s-shock-therapy-already-leaves-investors-craving-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
